ActSpecies at Risk Act
SubjectList of Wildlife Species at Risk (referral back to COSEWIC) Order
PrecisOrder (1) referring the assessment of the status of Yukon Draba (Draba yukonensis) back to the Committee on the Status of Endangered Wildlife in Canada (COSEWIC) for further consideration; and (2) approving the Minister of the Environment include in the public registry established under section 120 of the SPECIES AT RISK ACT the statement that is attached as the annex to this Order and that sets out the reasons for the referral back to COSEWIC.
